"title": "4113: angels, as agents of God's judgment",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4113",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Spiritual beings who assist God in carrying out his judgments. Angels will be especially active when Jesus Christ returns for the last judgment.</p>\n<h2>Angels as agents of earthly judgments</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:49\">PSA 78:49</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Against Sodom and Gomorrah</h3>\n<p><em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:13\">GEN 19:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:24-Gen19:25\">GEN 19:24–19:25</a></p>\n<h3>Against opponents of God</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:23\">EXO 12:23</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:35\">2KI 19:35</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:21\">2CH 32:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:36\">ISA 37:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:4-Ps35:6\">PSA 35:4–35:6</a></p>\n<h3>Against Israel</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:35\">EXO 32:35</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:16-2Sam24:17\">2SA 24:16–24:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:15-1Chr21:16\">1CH 21:15–21:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:10\">1CO 10:10</a></p>\n<h3>Against Herod Antipas</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:18-Acts12:23\">ACT 12:18–12:23</a></p>\n<h2>Angels restrained by God's mercy</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:15-1Chr21:16\">1CH 21:15–21:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam24:16-2Sam24:17\">2SA 24:16–24:17</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:20-Gen18:32\">GEN 18:20–18:32</a></p>\n<h2>Angels and final judgment</h2>\n<h3>Angels proclaim God's sovereignty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:10-Rev12:12\">REV 12:10–12:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:1-Rev10:4\">REV 10:1–10:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:15\">REV 11:15</a></p>\n<h3>Angels announce God's final invitation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:6-Rev14:7\">REV 14:6–14:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:9-Rev14:13\">REV 14:9–14:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:9\">REV 19:9</a></p>\n<h3>Angels hold back the final judgment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:1-Rev7:3\">REV 7:1–7:3</a></p>\n<h3>Angels carry out preliminary warning judgments</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:1-Rev8:13\">REV 8:1–8:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:1-Rev9:16\">REV 9:1–9:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:5-Rev10:7\">REV 10:5–10:7</a></p>\n<h3>Angels accompany Jesus Christ when he returns to judge</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess1:7\">2TH 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:27\">MAT 16:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:31\">MAT 25:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark8:38\">MRK 8:38</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:26\">LUK 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:13\">1TH 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Angels gather everyone for the final judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:37-Matt13:41\">MAT 13:37–13:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:49-Matt13:50\">MAT 13:49–13:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:31\">MAT 24:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:15-Rev14:19\">REV 14:15–14:19</a></p>\n<h3>Angels announce the final judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:15\">REV 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:8-Rev10:11\">REV 10:8–10:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:1-Rev17:3\">REV 17:1–17:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:7\">REV 17:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:15\">REV 17:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:1-Rev18:2\">REV 18:1–18:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:4\">REV 18:4</a></p>\n<h3>Angels enact the final judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:1\">REV 15:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev14:16-Rev14:19\">REV 14:16–14:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:6-Rev15:8\">REV 15:6–15:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:1-Rev16:21\">REV 16:1–16:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev18:21\">REV 18:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:17-Rev19:18\">REV 19:17–19:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:1-Rev20:3\">REV 20:1–20:3</a></p>\n<h2>Angels are subject to judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:3\">1CO 6:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:4\">2PE 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:6\">JUD 1:6</a></p>",
